Cell["\<\
Although it is not specified in the above example, it uses the coordinates of \
cities to measure distances. 

This can be seen by realising that the dendrogram obtained by explicitly \
using coordinates has the same topology as the one used without specifying \
the coordinates.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7811610582300825`*^9, 
  3.7811611563247423`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"825bc963-af33-41eb-a0d5-\
ea5ff96d7cb9"],

