Cell["\<\
One can visualise the probability that any point in the space is assigned to \
a certain class.

For example, the probability that any point (x,y) is assigned to class 2 is\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.781842195969043*^9, 
  3.781842266847356*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e301bc68-7fbe-4425-bab2-\
83c6ad43e0d7"],

